@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam classBorderColor #F57F17
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Draft
Draft --> Pending : update
Draft : entry / log hashtag
Pending --> Delivered : process
Delivered --> Closed : update
Delivered : entry / log hashtag
Closed --> Archived : approve
Closed : entry / log hashtag
Archived --> [*]
@enduml